<preface>
<title>Introduction</title>

<para>The <application>coffeepot</application> application is a small wrapper
around the underlying <package>CoffeeFilter</package> library which is, in turn,
a wrapper around the underlying <package>CoffeeGrinder</package> parser.</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><package>CoffeePot</package> is the command line interface.
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para><package>CoffeeFilter</package> is the Invisible XML library.
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para><package>CoffeeGrinder</package> is the Earley parser.
</para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>

<para><package>CoffeePot</package> marshals the grammar and inputs specified
into requests against the underlying libraries.</para>

</preface>

